history.content:
In phase 1, I enrolled in CS182, and then I requested a swap to CS189, but in waitlist. In phase 2, I dropped CS W182, which means the swap shouldn't be in effect anymore. And I added CS W182 again and was on the waitlist. A few days later, I was in CS W182, which should not be swapped to CS 189. A few days ago, CS 189 expanded, I was enrolled in CS189, and I got automatically dropped from CS W182. 

I think it shouldn't happen, and I should now be enrolled in both CS W182 and CS 189.
history.subject: I should be enrolled in CS W182.
